1121
01:22:09,130 --> 01:22:11,660
- ¿Que hora es?
- ¿Que hora es?

1122
01:22:11,730 --> 01:22:13,890
- Mấy giờ rồi?
- Mấy giờ rồi?

1123
01:22:13,970 --> 01:22:16,600
