1124
01:22:16,670 --> 01:22:18,610
Ngủ ngon em yêu.

1125
01:22:26,320 --> 01:22:28,250
Butch?

1126
01:22:34,160 --> 01:22:36,090
Thôi vậy.

1127
01:22:43,070 --> 01:22:45,690
Aah!

