1174
01:25:52,880 --> 01:25:54,810
Em có mà

1175
01:25:56,180 --> 01:25:58,120
Có chắc không?

1176
01:25:59,220 --> 01:26:01,150
Không

1177
01:26:03,260 --> 01:26:05,180
Khốn kiếp! Khốn kiếp! Khốn kiếp!

1178
01:26:05,260 --> 01:26:07,620
Đ. M!

1179
01:26:09,530 --> 01:26:12,330
